txt.en: 'I upheld my end of our trade, and now you had best do the same.'
'Do not think to threaten me, Rohirrim.'
'You and your friend are two among many here, and you would do well to remember that.'
'I do not know the name of the man you seek, but if you find his master, you shall find him.'
'The deal is made. I shall offer what I know of this man, and then you shall depart.'
'That is all I know. Now, begone... else I shall set my men upon you.'
'Head back to our camp, [placeholder]. I shall meet you there!'
'The man you seek is an agent of Mordor.'
'He serves a man named Cr√∫mgam, a sorcerer of the Eye.'
